And can anyone briefly explain what are these Hardware id's for?

For all those asking:

1) Follow the instructions in the Read Me (same instructions as given in file info above)
2) To get your hardware ID, run the game by clicking the exe.  It will download a patch.  Install that.  Afterwards, it will give you an option for activation.
3) Choose "manual" activation.  It will then give you your hardware ID, and ask for the key. 
4) Run the keygen in the Crack folder in the Venice iso, input the hardware ID you got, click 'Generate'.  Copy and paste the key into the Venice activation blank.  Grats, you can now play!

FYI: I ran the keygen through Nod32 and received no warnings about malware.
